{"tid":2120561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【星島賣盤】何柱國逢特首必鬧 轉軚撐梁振英最肉酸","createTime":"2020-07-22T18:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T19:07:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b459944d5c196875787c426f0c3127d809c7481","tid":2120561,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/finance/20200723/E2ZHP4VOPDFRTSCUBYGRBZEUAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200723%2FE2ZHP4VOPDFRTSCUBYGRBZEUAM%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=0f4545f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200723%2FE2ZHP4VOPDFRTSCUBYGRBZEUAM%2F&h=04050cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/finance/20200723/E2ZHP4VOPDFRTSCUBYGRBZEUAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n入主星島後，主席兼大股東何柱國多次高調論政，分別與幾屆特首均有過節，何高調論政的作風，在現任特首林鄭月娥時期最為激進，多次在旗下《星島日報》刊登全版頭版廣告，向林鄭發炮，直言香港目前困境，香港人如果能扛過去，是「香港人靠一己努力、韌力行番出來，並唔係靠特首帶領我哋」。去年更有傳言說，他正為下屆政府組班，他否認之餘，強調自己對做官無興趣。"},{"pid":"3f8d10913bb116d03439900f82c71e5ef5a5a8e3","tid":2120561,"uid":273703,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27a95fc67af75e56f83aae562fd70606c1ff44a9","tid":2120561,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8d10913bb116d03439900f82c71e5ef5a5a8e3","tid":2120561,"uid":273703,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49a40ee16c7329ec1e14919712aa8e5124e517